    vnoremap <buffer><silent> <LocalLeader>l  :<C-u>call Voof_Oop('left', 'v')<CR>
    vnoremap <buffer><silent>       <C-Left>  :<C-u>call Voof_Oop('left', 'v')<CR>
    vnoremap <buffer><silent>             <<  :<C-u>call Voof_Oop('left', 'v')<CR>

